        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nA very minor comment about your git commit messages - Andrew G. suggests this format:\n\nHeader line (< 50 char)\n\n[blank line]\n\nBody of message (as many as you like)\n\n[blank line]\n\nFooter with a line like \"Issue: PORTAL-38\".  The footer has a line with issue number, a line with the change-id, and a line with your signed-off code.  Pls note that the very last line MUST be the Signed-off-by line.\n\nHTH",
